profile.bio: I prefer Free & Open-Source Software and a free Internet. I am concerned about privacy and the power-creep over basic rights.  I'm an autodidact, transhuman, maker, coder, martial artist, sometimes philosopher, avid reader and terrible artist. Align=CN
